TITLE: Customizing Password Validation Rules in Laravel
DESCRIPTION: Code snippet demonstrating how to set custom password validation rules for Statamic users by modifying the default Password class in the AppServiceProvider. This example shows setting a 16-character minimum length requirement.

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Illuminate\Validation\Rules\Password;

public function boot()
{
    Password::defaults(function () {
        return Password::min(16);
    });
}
```

