TITLE: Example of Base EloquentQueryBuilder in Statamic
DESCRIPTION: A simplified version of Statamic's base EloquentQueryBuilder class that proxies methods to an Eloquent query builder and transforms the results into Statamic objects. It handles common query methods like get, first, and where.

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
abstract class EloquentQueryBuilder implements Builder
{
    protected $builder;

    public function __construct(EloquentBuilder $builder)
    {
        $this->builder = $builder;
    }

    public function __call($method, $args)
    {
        $this->builder->$method(...$args);

        return $this;
    }

    public function get($columns = ['*'])
    {
        $items = $this->builder->get($columns);

        return $this->transform($items, $columns);
    }

    public function first()
    {
        return $this->get()->first();
    }

    public function where($column, $operator = null, $value = null)
    {
        $this->builder->where($this->column($column), $operator, $value);

        return $this;
    }
}
```

