TITLE: Nginx Server Configuration for Static Caching
DESCRIPTION: Nginx server configuration to handle static caching with conditional rules for different request types and support for live preview.

LANGUAGE: nginx
CODE:
```
set $try_location @static;

if ($request_method != GET) {
    set $try_location @not_static;
}

if ($args ~* "live-preview=(.*)") {
    set $try_location @not_static;
}

location / {
    try_files $uri $try_location;
}

location @static {
    try_files /static${uri}_$args.html $uri $uri/ /index.php?$args;
}

location @not_static {
    try_files $uri /index.php?$args;
}
```

