TITLE: Alternative Migration Approach for v2 to v3 Fieldtypes
DESCRIPTION: This Vue component shows an alternative approach for migrating fieldtypes from Statamic v2 to v3 by adding a data property that initializes from the value prop and watching for changes to maintain compatibility with existing code.

LANGUAGE: vue
CODE:
```
<template>
    <input type="text" v-model="data" />
</template>
<script>
export default {
    mixins: [Fieldtype],
    data() {
        return {
            data: this.value,
        }
    },
    watch: {
        data(data) {
            this.update(data);
        }
    }
}
</script>
```

