TITLE: Managing Multi-site Entry Relations with Eloquent
DESCRIPTION: Implements methods to handle origin relationships for multi-site entries using Eloquent relationships rather than storing references in YAML data.

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
    public function origin($origin = null)
    {
        if (func_num_args() > 0) {
            $this->origin = $origin;

            return $this;
        }

        if ($this->origin) {
            return $this->origin;
        }

        if (! $this->model->origin) {
            return null;
        }

        return self::fromModel($this->model->origin);
    }

    public function originId()
    {
        return optional($this->origin)->id() ?? optional($this->model)->origin_id;
    }

    public function hasOrigin()
    {
        return $this->originId() !== null;
    }
}
```

