TITLE: Implementing ProvidesCommitMessage Interface for Custom Events in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Full implementation of a custom event class that implements the ProvidesCommitMessage interface. This allows the addon to provide a default commit message when content is saved and automatically committed to git.

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

namespace Punner\Events;

use Statamic\Contracts\Git\ProvidesCommitMessage;
use Statamic\Events\Event;

class PunSaved extends Event implements ProvidesCommitMessage
{
    public $item;

    public function __construct($item)
    {
        $this->item = $item;
    }

    public function commitMessage()
    {
        return __('Pun saved');
    }
}
```

