TITLE: Implementing Dynamic URL-based Template Loading in Statamic PHP
DESCRIPTION: A PHP route configuration that maps URLs directly to template files in your views directory. The code includes a homepage route and a dynamic route that matches any URL pattern to its corresponding template. This approach bypasses the need for collections and blueprints during initial development.

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
# routes/web.php

use Statamic\View\View;

Route::statamic('/', 'home');

Route::get('{template}', function ($template) {
    return View::make($template)->layout('layout');
})->where('template', '(?!cp).+');
```

